title.narrative: Provide Technical Assistance for Govenrment of Nepal

description.narrative: This activity (Provide Technical Assistance for Govenrment of Nepal) is a component of Skills for Employment Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £999,999. This component benefits Nepal, and works in the following sector(s): Vocational training. The start date is 11-01-2016 and the end date is 30-09-2022.
